## Enhanced PII Routing Switch ðŸ“Š

**What it does: **
Makes intelligent routing decisions based on analysis results

**Technology: **
n8n Switch Node with advanced rule logic

**3-Tier Decision Logic:**

**Tier 1: Critical PII - Local Only**
javascriptif (highestSeverity === 'critical' || riskScore > 2.0) {
  route = "Critical PII - Local Only"
  // SSNs, Medical IDs, Credit Cards, High-risk combinations
}

**Tier 2: Standard PII - Local Processing**
javascriptif (piiDetected === true || riskScore >= 1.5 || 
    context === 'medical' || context === 'financial') {
  route = "PII Detected - Local Processing"  
  // Any PII, sensitive contexts, medium-risk data
}

**Tier 3: Clean - Cloud Processing**
javascriptif (piiDetected === false && riskScore < 1.5) {
  route = "Clean - Cloud Processing"
  // No PII detected, safe for cloud processing
}

**Why This Approach Works:**

Granular Control: Not just binary PII/no-PII decisions
Context Awareness: Financial discussions stay local even without explicit PII
Risk-YOUR_OPENAI_KEY_HERE: Combines multiple factors for smarter routing
Compliance-First: Ensures sensitive contexts never reach cloud
